            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "A prophet from Shiloh. His words and actions challenged the authority of kings who disobeyed God. God used Ahijah to show that Solomon hadn’t been faithful to God’s covenant with David. Later God used Ahijah to show that Jeroboam hadn’t been faithful to God either."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    }
